title: King of Manifestations
summary: King of Manifestations Li Luo is Nan Feng Academy’s best student, outshining his peers. However, he was born without a Manifestation, causing him to fall behind his classmates. When Li Luo decides to use the solution his parents left behind to solve his problem, he fell into the adversity of “five years of service to the country, otherwise, he would die”. Between heaven and earth, there are Manifestations. And I, Li Luo, will become the King of Manifestations! Absolute Resonance King of Manifestations 万相之王
